    public abstract class VCardParameters.TypeParameterList<T extends VCardParameter>
extends VCardParameters.EnumParameterList<T>

    A list that converts the raw string values of a TYPE parameter to the appropriate VCardParameter object that some parameters use.

    This list is backed by the VCardParameters object. Any changes made to the list will affect the VCardParameters object and vice versa.
